Package: MEAT
Title: Muscle Epigenetic Age Test
Version: 0.99.3
Description: This package estimates epigenetic age in skeletal muscle,
    using DNA methylation data generated with
    Illumina Infinium technology (HM27, HM450 and HMEPIC).
